==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|abreptus|lang=la}}, perfect passive participle of {{m|la|abripiō||snatch away}}; from {{term|ab||away|lang=la}} + {{m|la|rapiō||snatch}}.

